---
import HQShell from '../layouts/HQShell.astro';
---
<HQShell title="Schedule Deployment" active="schedule">
  <section class="hero"><div class="hero-grid"><div><div class="kicker">Lake Area Adventures Booking</div><h1>Schedule Deployment</h1><p>Zombie Patrol HQ is the in-universe records and information terminal. Booking, payment, waivers, and official guest transactions stay with Lake Area Adventures.</p><div class="btn-row"><a class="btn hot" href="https://lakeareaadventures.centeredgeonline.com/event/events">Open Party Booking</a><a class="btn" href="/training-center">Review Training Center</a></div></div><img class="hero-logo" src="/assets/logos/lake-area-adventures-logo.png" alt="Lake Area Adventures" /></div></section>
  <div class="panel-grid"><section class="panel span-6"><h2>Before You Deploy</h2><p>Check the official Lake Area Adventures booking page for current availability, pricing, waivers, and party options.</p></section><section class="panel span-6"><h2>Public Records</h2><p>After games are imported and approved in Annelle, public-safe training records can appear here through the future hourly snapshot sync.</p></section></div>
</HQShell>
